Genitalia (
Fig. 10 B–F
). Gonocoxite low, without posterior projection, with 3 strong and 5 medium to weak setae. Tergite IX divided, with altogether about 22 setae. Cercus 101–103 µm long. Apodeme against gonocoxite 82–101 µm long. Segment X with long, sharp posterolateral corners. Seminal capsule 75–89 µm long, 75 µm (1) wide, microtrichia not observed, spermathecal ducts with loop, without bulbs before common opening. Notum 82– 105 µm long.
